{
  "texts": [
    "Zou et al. (2019) adapt an ML model to detect gestures using Wi-Fi CSI data between two rooms in a building.",
    "Such applications involving transfer learning between domains has been explored in the application of occupancy and activity sensing in several other literature studies (e.g., Pan et al., 2008; Khalil et al., 2021; Li et al., 2021; Dridi et al., 2022; Omeragic et al., 2023).",
    "Pinto et al. (2022) delve further into a review of transfer learning application in smart buildings.",
    "To summarize, ML methods have been proposed to map the relation between data from sensors, and occupancy/activity.",
    "Once trained, these models can then be deployed to predict the occupancy which then gets fed to building control mechanisms (Esrafilian-Najafabadi and Haghighat, 2021)."
  ]
}